003, 2006.","meanings":["Hugues Capet  (  ?938–96 ) was ruler of France (  987–96 ) and founder of the Capetian dynasty.  See  <b>Hugh</b> ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Hugues des Baux seigneur de Gaudissart was born about 1285, in Italy, his father, seigneur de Courthezon Bertrand des Baux d'Orange III, was 47 and his mother, Étiennette des Baux-d'Orange, was 31. He married Jacopa della Marra in 1302. They were the parents of at least 1 son and 1 daughter. He died in 1315, in Tanaron, Alpes-de-Haute-Provence, Provence-Alpes-Côte d'Azur, France, at the age of 31, and was buried in Alessandria, Piedmont, Italy."},"et":{"about 1285–1315":"umbes 1285–1315","1272–1328":"1272–1328","1285–1315":"1285–1315","1275–1312":"1275–1312","1296–1375":"1296–1375","1305–1375":"1305–1375","1240–1305":"1240–1305","1255–1301":"1255–1301","before 1301":"enne 1301","about 1270":"umbes 1270","1275":"1275","1296":"1296","1285":"1285","1240":"1240","AFT 10 DEC 1319":"pärast 10. detsembrit 1319","1272":"1272","aft 1312":"pärast 1312","1305":"1305","1315":"1315","1302":"1302","1301":"1301","1312":"1312","1255":"1255","1375":"1375","about 1285":"umbes 1285","ABT 1270":"umbes 1270","1328":"1328","Puglia, Italia":"Puglia, Itaalia","Italy":"Itaalia","Battle of Tanaro":"Tanaron, Alpes-de-Haute-Provence, Provence-Alpes-Côte d'Azur, Prantsusmaa","Alessandria (Alexandrie),,Alexandrie,Piémont,Italie,":"Alessandria, Piemonte, Itaalia","Palestine":"Palestiina"},"fi":{"about 1285–1315":"noin 1285–1315","1272–1328":"1272–1328","1285–1315":"1285–1315","1275–1312":"1275–1312","1296–1375":"1296–1375","1305–1375":"1305–1375","1240–1305":"1240–1305","1255–1301":"1255–1301","before 1301":"ennen vuotta 1301","about 1270":"noin 1270","1275":"1275","1296":"1296","1285":"1285","1240":"1240","AFT 10 DEC 1319":"10. joulukuuta 1319 jälkeen","1272":"1272","aft 1312":"1312 jälkeen","1305":"1305","1315":"1315","1302":"1302","1301":"1301","1312":"1312","1255":"1255","1375":"1375","about 1285":"noin 1285","ABT 12